<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home - Plaidypus Client</title>
  <link href="/public/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-plaid-light-gray min-h-screen">
  <%- include('partials/navigation', { tokens, currentPage: 'home' }) %>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-plaid-black">Core Exchange API Playground</h1>
        <p class="text-plaid-dark-gray mt-2">Time to kick the tires on Core Exchange!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- About Section -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 p-6 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-plaid-black mb-4">What's Under the Hood</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-plaid-dark-gray">
          <p class="mb-3">
            A full-stack reference implementation of <strong>Core Exchange API v6.3</strong> with
            proper OAuth 2.0 + OpenID Connect flows. Everything you need to build secure, modern financial integrations.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-3">
            The three-service architecture:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-3">
            <li><strong>Authorization Server</strong> - OIDC Provider juggling auth flows and minting tokens</li>
            <li><strong>Resource Server (API)</strong> - JWT-protected API serving up financial data like it's 2025</li>
            <li><strong>Client App (RP)</strong> - This guy right here, doing the PKCE dance and making authenticated
              requests</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Once you're authenticated, explore the API Explorer to test every endpoint and see sample data
            flowing through a production-ready architecture. You've got this.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if (!tokens) { %>
        <!-- Get Started (Signed Out) -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-plaid-mint-200 to-plaid-blue-sky-200 rounded-lg border border-plaid-mint-200 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-plaid-mint-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z">
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plaid-black mb-2">Ready to Authenticate?</h3>
          <p class="text-plaid-dark-gray mb-6">Fire up an OAuth flow and get yourself some shiny JWT tokens</p>
          <a href="/login"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-plaid-mint-600 border border-transparent rounded-md text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-plaid-mint-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                d="M11 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h14m-5 4v1a3 3 0 01-3 3H6a3 3 0 01-3-3V7a3 3 0 013-3h7a3 3 0 013 3v1"></path>
            </svg>
            Start the OIDC Flow
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-plaid-gray mt-4">
            Test credentials: <code class="bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded">user@example.test</code> /
            <code class="bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded">passw0rd!</code>
          </p>
        </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <!-- Quick Actions (Signed In) -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 p-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-plaid-black mb-4">Quick Actions</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <a href="/api-explorer"
                class="flex items-start p-4 border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 rounded-lg hover:border-plaid-mint-200 hover:bg-plaid-mint-200 transition-colors group">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-plaid-mint-600 group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700" fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700">API Explorer</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray mt-1">Test every endpoint right in your browser,
                    authenticated and ready to go</p>
                </div>
              </a>

              <a href="/me"
                class="flex items-start p-4 border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 rounded-lg hover:border-plaid-mint-200 hover:bg-plaid-mint-200 transition-colors group">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-plaid-mint-600 group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700" fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700">Token Inspector
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray mt-1">Decode your ID token and see what claims you're carrying
                    around</p>
                </div>
              </a>

              <a href="/accounts"
                class="flex items-start p-4 border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 rounded-lg hover:border-plaid-mint-200 hover:bg-plaid-mint-200 transition-colors group">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-plaid-mint-600 group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700" fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black group-hover:text-plaid-mint-700">Quick Smoke Test
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray mt-1">Hit <code>/accounts</code> and watch the magic happen</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% } %>

            <!-- Features Section -->
            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-plaid-mint-200 rounded-lg mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-plaid-mint-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z">
                    </path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black mb-2">Battle-Tested Auth</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray">OAuth 2.0 + OIDC with PKCE</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-plaid-credit-lime-200 rounded-lg mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-plaid-credit-lime-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z">
                    </path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black mb-2">Spec-Compliant APIs</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray">100% Core Exchange v6.3</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-plaid-blue-sky-200 p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-plaid-royal-purple-200 rounded-lg mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-plaid-royal-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15">
                    </path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-plaid-black mb-2">Long-Lived Sessions</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-plaid-dark-gray">Refresh tokens for when you need that sweet, sweet
                  <code>offline_access</code>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>